The paper deals with generating photo-realistic images from semantic label maps, which is a problem in computer vision (CV). The use of edge maps and Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) also suggests a focus on graphics (GR) and multimedia (MM). The paper also involves training the GAN, which falls under machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI).
